Package: isoformnspectRe
Type: Package
Title: Companion package of a nextflow pipeline
Version: 0.1.3
Author: 47Lies
Maintainer: 47Lies <lieng.taing@gmail.com>
Description: Companion R package for the isoandspe nextflow pipeline
    It will allow several task
    The main one is the shiny app that allow exploration of the pipeline results
    It will exploit a series of files from the pipeline that will generate r markdown html report on a protein found with the pipeline.
